            . On the 8th of August, about half-past ten o'clock in the morning, I was by the side of the <placeName id="t18190915-255-crimeloc1374">New River at Islington</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18190915-255-crimeloc1374" type="placeName" value="New River at Islington"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18190915-255-crimeloc1374" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18190915-255-off1372 t18190915-255-crimeloc1374"></join>, and found the two prisoners at my heels - I turned round, and caught Bird concealing my handkerchief, which he had taken from my pocket, I seized him, and charged him with picking my pocket - he said it was not him, it was the other boy gave it to him. We took them both to the watch-house, and gave them in charge.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18190915-255-person2176">
                  ROBERT 
                  BROWN
               <interp inst="t18190915-255-person2176" type="surname" value="BROWN"></interp>
