                     <interp inst="t18190915-255-person2176" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I took the prisoners in charge. Allen said he took the handkerchief and gave it to Bird.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>ALLEN'S Defence. I saw it on the ground and picked it up - Bird cried</p>
               <p>"Halves!" I gave it to him, and the prosecutor collared us.</p>
